  65:src/voice.h   ****   // in the first few ms) scales loudness. 0 = fixed loudness (default ŌĆö the
  66:src/voice.h   ****   // sustained instruments); ~0.85 on drums for accents/ghost notes. Loudness
  67:src/voice.h   ****   // floor = (1 - vel_sens), so soft taps stay audible.
