 807:src/voice.h   **** // Drums: when true, every tap is treated as full (100%) pressure ŌĆö consistent
 808:src/voice.h   **** // hits regardless of how hard the glass reads. Set false for velocity dynamics
 809:src/voice.h   **** // (uses the drum's vel_sens). Drums only.
