 678:src/main.cpp  ****             // ŌöĆŌöĆ Moog-style exponential cutoff ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌö
 679:src/main.cpp  ****             // At zero pressure: cutoff = 0.5x pitch (below fundamental, very dark)
 680:src/main.cpp  ****             // At full pressure: cutoff = 0.5x * 2^(6*prs) ŌĆö exponential opening
 681:src/main.cpp  ****             // 6 octaves of sweep = factor of 64x, so fully open = 32x pitch
 682:src/main.cpp  ****             // This gives the classic Moog "closed ŌåÆ wah ŌåÆ bright" feel.
 683:src/main.cpp  ****             // Power-3 on pressure so the bottom half stays dark and controlled.
 684:src/main.cpp  ****             // ŌöĆŌöĆ Smootherstep pressure curves (6xŌüĄ - 15xŌü┤ + 10x┬│) ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌö
 685:src/main.cpp  ****             // Starts slow, steep in the middle, eases gently at the top.
 686:src/main.cpp  ****             // Much more playable than power curves ŌĆö feels like a real knob.
